    <h2 id="Preview">Preview Animations</h2>

    <p>Use the Play button below the canvas to play all animations on the page directly within the editor.</p>

    <p class="img-wrap">
      <amp-img layout="intrinsic" width="277" height="139" src="./img/docs/how-to/play-animations.png"></amp-img>
